In the MDD method, the simulation database established by CFD and the monitor database of the sensor are used to identify the location of the unknown source by calculating the discrete degree between the two databases. The MDD method is to calculate the least concentration difference between the unknown and the potential sources. Performance of the MDD method can be improved by introducing a new virtual source α
p′ to represent the concentration difference between the unknown source and the potential sample source. The item of concentration difference c
